<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Patch 37 (October 21, 2014)</h4><ul><li><b>Salous now has a passive: Inner Calm, Outer Storm (Passive)</b></li><ul><li> Salous's Movement Speed is increased by between 8% and 20% based on the number of enemy Shapers he has damaged with a basic attack or ability in the last 5 seconds.</li></ul><li><b>Judgment (Q)</b></li><ul><li> The initial hit base damage of this ability has been reduced to 30/45/60/75/90, down from 35/50/65/80/95.</li><li> The secondary activation damage of this ability has been reduced to 70/85/100/115/130, down from 75/90/105/120/135.</li></ul><li><b>Spirit Seals (W)</b></li><ul><li> This ability is now additionally tagged as "Damage Over Time" in addition to "Area of Effect".</li></ul><li><b>Penance (E)</b></li><ul><li> The base damage of this ability has been reduced to 50/85/120/155/190, down from 70/110/150/190/230.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 30 (May 27th, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Spirit Seals (W)</B></li><ul><li>The base damage per orb on this ability has been reduced to 30/45/60/75/90, down from 35/50/65/80/95.</li></ul><li><B>Absolution (R)</B></li><ul><li>The base damage on this ability has been adjusted to 150/225/300, from 150/250/350.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 28 (April 8, 2014)</h4><ul><li><B>Judgment (Q)</B></li><ul><li>The projectile speed of this ability has been reduced to 1800, down from 2040.</li></ul><li><B>Spirit Seals (W)</B></li><ul><li>The base damage of this ability per orb has been reduced to 35/50/65/80/95, down from 40/55/70/85/100.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 27 (March 17, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Judgment (Q)</li><ul><li>The range of this ability has been increased to 1000, up from 950.</li><li>The projectile speed of this ability has been increased to 60, up from 45.</li></ul><li>Penance (E)</li><ul><li>The root duration of this ability has been increased to 1.5 seconds, up from 1.35.</li></ul><li>Absolution (R)</li><ul><li>Fixed a bug where the tooltip did not correctly specify the duration of the slow applied by this ability.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>Judgment (Q)</li><ul><li>The range of this ability has been increased by 11%.</li></ul><li>Spirit Seals (W)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 500, from previous value of 550.</li><li>The radius in which the orbs on this ability will detonate has been increased to 125, up from 80.</li></ul><li>Penance (E)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 170, from previous value of 190.</li></ul><li>Absolution (R)</li><ul><li>The displayed range of this ability has been updated to 680, from previous value of 760.</li><li>The Power ratio of this ability has been reduced to 0.6, down from 0.75.</li></ul></ul><h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 18 (November 21, 2013)</h4><ul><li><B>Judgment (Q)</B></li><ul><li>Added some tooltip clarity to this ability to further describe the targeting function of this ability.</li></ul><li><B>Absolution (R)</B></li><ul><li>Added a new targeting icon for this ultimate ability so players may now effectively see the range at which targets affected will be stunned and the correct cone in which this ultimate ability will slow targets affected.</li></ul></ul>